@startuml seq_realtime_notification
!theme plain
title Sequence Diagram: Real-time Notification Broadcasting

skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Admin/Manager" as Admin
participant "React SPA (Sender)" as ClientAdmin
participant "Kong API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Noti Service" as Noti
database "PostgreSQL (HA)" as PG
database "MongoDB" as Mongo
participant "Socket.IO / Redis" as Socket
participant "React SPA (Receiver)" as ClientUser

Admin -> ClientAdmin : Compose Announcement & Send
ClientAdmin -> Gateway : POST /api/noti/announcements \n(title, content, target)
Gateway -> Noti : Route Request

Noti -> Noti : Verify JWT & Check Permissions
Noti -> PG : INSERT INTO announcements \n(Save business data)
Noti -> Mongo : INSERT NotificationLog \n(Action: 'SENT' Audit Trail)

Noti -> Socket : io.emit("new_announcement", payload)
Noti -> ClientAdmin : 201 Created (Sent successfully)
ClientAdmin -> Admin : Show Success Toast

Socket -> ClientUser : Receive Event "new_announcement"
ClientUser -> ClientUser : Check Target Rule (Role, Dept, Email) & Increment Unread Badge
@enduml